<p>Fake Google reviews are a reality of doing business online. You cannot prevent them. You can identify them, report them, respond professionally, and bury them under a mountain of real positive reviews. The businesses that treat review management as an ongoing process, not a one-time fix, protect both their reputation and their search rankings.</p>
